{"tid":919899,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"河北張家口大爆炸釀44死傷　化工廠稱非廠房爆炸","createTime":"2018-11-28T11:46:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-28T15:27:36.000Z","uid":48083,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"6dcbe5b88979e91c956436535111894e7402618c","tid":919899,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T11:46:43.000Z","msg":"片:<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20181128/1474619/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20181128%2F1474619%2F&d=fPWMuOvQh280tnIgzO8zYpUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=dbc0b9c8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20181128%2F1474619%2F&h=643bb9e3\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20181128/1474619/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181128/640_f8b60b7268ebc9b96ee82a49a989b03f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181128%2F640_f8b60b7268ebc9b96ee82a49a989b03f.jpg&h=cd45d3ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國大陸河北張家口一間化工廠附近今日零時41分突然發生爆炸起火事件，奪走至少22條人命，另有22人受傷。據報導，現場有50輛車被燒毀，目前起火原因不明。<br />\n <br />\n張家口市橋東區河北盛華化工有限公司附近，發生一宗爆炸事件。公安消防搜救後指出，事故造成至少22死22傷。22名傷者已分別送往河北北方學院第一醫院和251等醫院救治。<br />\n <br />\n網上影片顯示，現場火光熊熊，濃煙沖天；醫院內有多名傷者等候救治，部份人手、腳、臉部被熏黑。<br />\n<br />\n盛華化工廠工作人員稱爆炸發生地並非其所在公司，而是在公司附近的馬路上，但具體詳細地點尚不清楚。工作人員稱，目前公司員工均正常上班，但已經暫時停產，「我們也是危險單位，因為不知道爆炸原因，所以現在不敢生產。」工作人員稱她看到馬路上有車輛損壞，爆炸造成的其他影響目前還不清楚。<br />\n<br />\n目前現場已無明火。經初步調查，共有50車被燒毀，包括大貨車38輛、小型車12輛。現場搜救工作和事故原因調查仍在進行中。（大陸中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n發稿時間：08:58<br />\n更新時間：11:01<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20181128/1474619/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20181128%2F1474619%2F&d=fPWMuOvQh280tnIgzO8zYpUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=dbc0b9c8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20181128%2F1474619%2F&h=643bb9e3\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20181128/1474619/</a>"},{"pid":"54f12b3661bfc10e1e210d8709e6d39a2e392d31","tid":919899,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T11:47:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a769108498be5bf6893215e1864ee610dd665b6","tid":919899,"uid":3063,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T11:49:19.000Z","msg":"華化工廠工作人員稱爆炸發生地並非其所在公司，而是在公司附近的馬路上<br />\n<br />\n馬路自爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1a1480938e1775213108280eea202aa4286c23a","tid":919899,"uid":42188,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T11:50:14.000Z","msg":"一定係佔中搞到咁"},{"pid":"cd5b2c783ce2cdf5d6f618d9629d402579d5cada","tid":919899,"uid":81113,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2a769108498be5bf6893215e1864ee610dd665b6","tid":919899,"uid":3063,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T11:49:19.000Z","msg":"華化工廠工作人員稱爆炸發生地並非其所在公司，而是在公司附近的馬路上<br />\n<br />\n馬路自爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T11:50:32.000Z","msg":"😂🤣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7de4a53984b4901663ce42bc3deb512fe05219a5","tid":919899,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0